{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-12809/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-12809"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:28:09"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["low key"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A dark room with an emoty chair"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-12809","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-12809"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/canvas/1/3f529e91-bae6-4896-ac66-8bd0d531bd07","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:12:05.994Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In a quite unusual opening shot for this scene, PTA features an empty chair in Reynolds’s room. The framing would suggest that there should be someone sitting in the chair—another phantom—particularly given how the scene cuts away to a close-up on Reynolds’s face, showing us that he has had his eyes closed and hasn’t been watching the chair and wall in front of him. Instead, it’s as if something or someone from that space will awaken him.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12809/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:783.1168831168832,394.2857142857143,780.7792207792209,635.8441558441559"}}}]}]}]}